Enum UiGradient

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<UiGradient>
      • org.pepstock.charba.client.colors.UiGradient
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<UiGradient>

    public enum UiGradient
extends Enum<UiGradient>
    uiGradients is a community contributed collection of beautiful multi-color gradients.
    Enumerates the uiGradients items, with a set of predefined colors, in order to create Charba Gradients.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero
